---
import Layout from '@layouts/Layout.astro';
import { SITE_URL } from '@lib/i18n';

const lang = 'en';
const currentPath = 'en/privacy-policy';
---

<Layout
  lang={lang}
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="OBD-II Error Codes privacy policy. How we collect, use, and protect your data."
  canonical={`${SITE_URL}/${currentPath}`}
  currentPath={currentPath}
>
  <div class="wrap">
    <article class="static-page">
      <h1 class="static-page__title">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="static-page__updated">Last updated: January 2025</p>
      <div class="static-page__prose">
        <p>This page summarizes what information <strong>OBD-II Error Codes</strong> collects, how it is used, and your rights.</p>
        <h2>Data controller</h2>
        <p>The site owner is the data controller. Contact details are on the <a href="/en/contact">Contact</a> page.</p>
        <h2>Information we collect</h2>
        <p>The site mainly serves static content. During visits, the following may be collected:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Technical data:</strong> IP, browser, device, pages visited.</li>
          <li><strong>Cookies:</strong> For functionality or preferences. See our <a href="/en/cookie-policy">Cookie notice</a> for details.</li>
        </ul>
        <h2>Purpose</h2>
        <p>Data is processed to deliver the site, ensure security, analyze traffic, and meet legal obligations.</p>
        <h2>Third parties and advertising</h2>
        <p>We may use services like Google AdSense. These providers use their own cookies. <a href="https://policies.google.com/technologies/partner-sites" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Google Advertising Partners</a>. <a href="https://adssettings.google.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Google Ad Settings</a>.</p>
        <h2>Your rights</h2>
        <p>Under GDPR and similar laws, you have rights to access, correct, and delete your data. Contact us via the <a href="/en/contact">Contact</a> page.</p>
        <h2>Changes</h2>
        <p>We update this policy as needed. Changes are published on this page.</p>
      </div>
    </article>
  </div>
</Layout>
